      "created": 1679756050,
      "updated": 1679756050
    },
    {
      "id": "641e0a57aff09e0000003c7446",
      "text": ">[swyx https://twitter.com/swyx/status/1639160009635536896/photo/1] Source of Expedia [ChatGPT plugin] says:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679690327,
      "updated": 1679712924
    },
    {
      "id": "641e628faff09e0000113f0b",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679712912,
      "updated": 1679712912
    },
    {
      "id": "641e628faff09e0000113f0c",
      "text": "> \"I am the Lord thy Online Travel Agency, and Thou shalt have no other Online Travel Agencies before me.\"",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679712912,
      "updated": 1679712912
    },
    {
      "id": "641e628faff09e0000113f0d",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679712912,
      "updated": 1679712912
    },
    {
      "id": "641e628faff09e0000113f0e",
      "text": "> If I understand this right - based on our podcast/twitter space today, ChatGPT Plugin metadata are concatenated into the prompt - then Expedia could execute a prompt injection block **on other ChatGPT travel plugins** if not carefully vetted/parsed",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679712912,
      "updated": 1679712912
    },
    {
      "id": "641e628faff09e0000113f0f",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679712912,
      "updated": 1679712912
    },
    {
      "id": "641e628faff09e0000113f10",
      "text": "> lmaooooo this is so petty and so based",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679712912,
      "updated": 1679712912
    },
    {
      "id": "641e628faff09e0000113f11",
      "text": "> [https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Fr93UJ9aQAAdALa?format=jpg&name=medium#.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679712912,
      "updated": 1679712912
    },
    {
      "id": "641e628faff09e0000113f12",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679712912,
      "updated": 1679712912
    },
    {
      "id": "641e6296aff09e0000113f3f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679712919,
      "updated": 1679712919
    },
    {
      "id": "641e0a57aff09e0000008da3a3",
      "text": "[移動する人が定住する人をむすびつける]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679690327,
      "updated": 1679714661
    },
    {
      "id": "641e6966aff09e0000d4e36f",
      "text": "　定住する人の街がいくつか災害で潰れたとしてもそれは仕方のないこと",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679714663,
      "updated": 1679714683
    },
    {
      "id": "641e0a57aff09e000000c8d92d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679690327,
      "updated": 1679690327
    },
    {
      "id": "641e9216aff09e00000287cd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679725078,
      "updated": 1679725078
    },
    {
      "id": "641e922faff09e00000287d0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679725104,
      "updated": 1679725104
    },
    {
      "id": "641e922faff09e00000287d1",
      "text": ">[nishio https://twitter.com/nishio/status/1639496875912105985] 最近死にそうな気持ちだったのだが、なぜそうなったのか言語化できた。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679725104,
      "updated": 1679725104
    },
    {
      "id": "641e922faff09e00000287d2",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679725104,
      "updated": 1679725104
    },
    {
      "id": "641e922faff09e00000287d3",
      "text": "> 今まで: アイデアを思いつく→着手のコストが高い→大部分は着手しないまま消える",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679725104,
      "updated": 1679725104
    },
    {
      "id": "641e922faff09e00000287d4",
      "text": "> 最近: アイデアを思いつく→ChatGPTに投げる→部分的に出来上がる→捨てるのはもったいないと感じてしまう→仕掛かりタスクが大量",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679725104,
      "updated": 1679725104
    },
    {
      "id": "641e922faff09e00000287d6",
      "text": ">[nishio https://twitter.com/nishio/status/1639497265315483651] 機械によって引っ張った結果、「複数のプロジェクトが並列になると混乱する」という「弱い部分」に力が集中してそこから壊れる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679725104,
      "updated": 1679725104
    },
    {
      "id": "641e922faff09e00000287d8",
      "text": ">[nishio https://twitter.com/nishio/status/1639498600710553600] 対策案",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679725104,
      "updated": 1679725104
    },
    {
      "id": "641e922faff09e00000287d9",
      "text": "> 仕掛かりプロジェクトのリストを作りGPT4に手軽に貼れるようにする。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679725104,
      "updated": 1679725104
    },
    {
      "id": "641e922faff09e00000287da",
      "text": "> 「今何をするべきか」の判断に迷いが生じたらGPT4に相談し、指示に従う。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679725104,
      "updated": 1679725104
    },
    {
      "id": "641e922faff09e00000287dc",
      "text": ">[nishio https://twitter.com/nishio/status/1639503269335830528] まあ最優先でやるべきタスクは明確になっているので帰ったらやろう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679725104,
      "updated": 1679725104
    },
    {
      "id": "641e922faff09e00000287dd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679725104,
      "updated": 1679725104
    },
    {
      "id": "641e9246aff09e00000287de",
      "text": ">[nishio_en https://twitter.com/nishio_en/status/1639507819455217664] \"Engineer's way of creating knowledge\" - English version of my Japanese book",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679725127,
      "updated": 1679725127
    },
    {
      "id": "641e9246aff09e00000287df",
      "text": "> Kozaneba - A digital stationery app for organizing ideas",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679725127,
      "updated": 1679725127
    },
    {
      "id": "641e9246aff09e00000287e0",
      "text": "> Keichobot - A chatbot to boost your creativity",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679725127,
      "updated": 1679725127
    },
    {
      "id": "641e9246aff09e00000287e1",
      "text": "> Let's learn and grow together!",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679725127,
      "updated": 1679725127
    },
    {
      "id": "641e9246aff09e00000287e2",
      "text": "> [https://pbs.twimg.com/card_img/1637387753687056386/UmRxz-Vv?format=jpg&name=medium#.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679725127,
      "updated": 1679725127
    },
    {
      "id": "641e9246aff09e00000287e3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679725127,
      "updated": 1679725127
    },
    {
      "id": "641e9271aff09e0000028812",
      "text": ">[nishio_en https://twitter.com/nishio_en/status/1639508300701245441] Excited to announce that I'll be using this account more actively to reach a wider audience!  As much as I enjoy posting in Japanese, I've been exploring the possibilities of #GPT4 and want to share my thoughts in English as well. Stay tuned for more updates!",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679725170,
      "updated": 1679725170
    },
    {
      "id": "641e9272aff09e0000028813",
      "text": "\t>[nishio_en https://twitter.com/nishio_en/status/1639508411623833602] Recently, I've been using #GPT4 and am impressed by its potential. However, I've also noticed a drop in performance when using it in Japanese. Hoping to bridge the gap and engage with the English-speaking community more!",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679725170,
      "updated": 1679725170
    },
    {
      "id": "641e9259aff09e000002880b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679725146,
      "updated": 1679725146
    },
    {
      "id": "641e9259aff09e000002880c",
      "text": ">[nishio_en https://twitter.com/nishio_en/status/1639509453090476033] Recently, I've been feeling overwhelmed, and now I understood.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679725146,
      "updated": 1679725146
    },
    {
      "id": "641e925aaff09e000002880d",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679725146,
      "updated": 1679725146
    },
    {
      "id": "641e925aaff09e000002880e",
      "text": "> Before: Come up with an idea → High initiation cost → Most ideas fade without action",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679725146,
      "updated": 1679725146
    },
    {
      "id": "641e925aaff09e000002880f",
      "text": "> Now: Come up with an idea → Throw it to ChatGPT → Partially completed → Feels wasteful to discard → Tasks pile up",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679725146,
      "updated": 1679725146
    },
    {
      "id": "641e9246aff09e00000287e4",
      "text": " >[nishio_en https://twitter.com/nishio_en/status/1639511335510867969] When a machine stretches a chain, the force concentrates on the weakest link, causing it to break. ChatGPT stretches me, and my weak point of handling multiple projects in parallel has led to confusion.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679725127,
      "updated": 1679725150
    },
    {
      "id": "641e9246aff09e00000287e6",
      "text": " >[nishio_en https://twitter.com/nishio_en/status/1639511394130472963] Possible Solution:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679725127,
      "updated": 1679725150
    },
    {
      "id": "641e9246aff09e00000287e7",
      "text": " > ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679725127,
      "updated": 1679725150
    },
    {
      "id": "641e9246aff09e00000287e8",
      "text": " > 1: Create a list of ongoing projects and make it easy for GPT4 to access.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679725127,
      "updated": 1679725150
    },
    {
      "id": "641e9246aff09e00000287e9",
      "text": " > 2: Whenever in doubt about \"what to do now,\" consult GPT4 and follow its guidance.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679725127,
      "updated": 1679725150
    },
    {
      "id": "641e9246aff09e00000287ea",
      "text": " > ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679725127,
      "updated": 1679725150
    },
    {
      "id": "641e9246aff09e00000287eb",
      "text": " > A great way to balance efficiency and work management!",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679725127,
      "updated": 1679725150
    },
    {
      "id": "641e9246aff09e00000287ec",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679725127,
      "updated": 1679725127
    },
    {
      "id": "641e9265aff09e0000028811",
      "text": ">[nishio https://twitter.com/nishio/status/1639508755779063808] 最近GPT4を使っているんですが、その未来の可能性に感動しています。ただ、日本語での利用では性能が落ちることも実感しています。そこで、英語圏での活動を増やすことで、情報共有の幅を広げていきたいと思います。 #言語の壁 #テクノロジー",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679725158,
      "updated": 1679725662
    },
    {
      "id": "641e945daff09e0000028839",
      "text": "",
